history.content:
The UC Berkeley Cloud Community of Practice's 21st meetup (and the first one for 2021!) will be held at a new date & time we will use while events remain virtual. The new time, the last Thursdays of the month at 1pm is the result of community feedback, and more conducive to virtual participation from people nationally.

CONNECT VIA ZOOM: Our Zoom connection info changes each month and is posted here in meetup invite.

RSVP: https://www.meetup.com/ucberkeley_cloudmeetup/events/275913376/
history.subject: UC Berkeley Cloud Meetup 021 (VIRTUAL)
